text: Biz () is a rural locality (a village) in Aksaitovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 87 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 8 km from Aksaitovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Biz, Republic of Bashkortostan
